OL,4,CBet365 boss earns #469m in a single
OL,5,Cyear
OL,6, The boss of the gambling firm Bet365
OL,7, has been awarded one of the biggest pay
OL,8, packets in UK corporate history.
OL,10,FThe highest paid director of Bet365
OL,11,FGroup - believed to be founder and
OL,12,Fmajority shareholder Denise Coates CBE
OL,13,F- earned a salary of #421m in the year
OL,14,Fending 29 March.
OL,16,FShe also earned #48m in dividends,
OL,17,Ftaking her total pay to #469m.
OL,19,FThe company said the arrangements were
OL,20,F"appropriate and fair", despite sales
OL,21,Ffalling at the firm last year.
